  "detailed_description": "<h1>Full Release Now</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players in the testing branch please <strong><u>switch back to the default branch</u></strong> to enjoy the version 1.0.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To switch:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go to your library, right-click <i>The World of Kungfu: Dragon and Eagle</i>, select \"Properties\" > \"Betas,\" and choose <strong>NONE</strong> from the dropdown menu.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/ffdb3dfbefe56fa1f3a3228bb173058d.poster.avif?t=1741226613\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/ffdb3dfbefe56fa1f3a3228bb173058d.webm?t=1741226613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>You had once stayed up past your bedtimes, huddled under covers, living the RPGs on SNES whose stories have stuck with you till today? Same for us! So much so that we’ve created an old-school Wuxia game with comparable features: strategic character leveling, turn-based combats, and most importantly, a vast array of characters and a gripping, heartfelt story.<br><br><strong>MAKE YOUR OWN NAME IN THE CHANGEABLE WULIN</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/d780724434f4a14f7077861488c4e4d5.poster.avif?t=1741226613\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/d780724434f4a14f7077861488c4e4d5.webm?t=1741226613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/d780724434f4a14f7077861488c4e4d5.mp4?t=1741226613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Harness and master the disciplines of martial arts, and make friends with a diverse cast of memorable characters along the way. Make a name for yourself and navigate difficult decisions that’ll forever change the course of the world.<br><br><strong>AN EXPANSIVE CAST OF DYNAMIC CHARACTERS</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/a00dd8a06f793e363cf88cde2d261f4c.poster.avif?t=1741226613\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/a00dd8a06f793e363cf88cde2d261f4c.webm?t=1741226613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Meet feuding clans and sects, brave patriots, twisted villains, and gruff old masters with remarkable kungfu skills.<br><br><strong>THE FATE OF JIANGHU RESTS IN YOUR HAND</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/07fa99a83cd177d67f930cb8e257b6c8.poster.avif?t=1741226613\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/07fa99a83cd177d67f930cb8e257b6c8.webm?t=1741226613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/07fa99a83cd177d67f930cb8e257b6c8.mp4?t=1741226613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Face moral dilemmas, beyond simple choices of good versus evil, shaping both you and the path you’ll tread. Will you align with the court’s agents or the street heroes? Would you make “minor” moral sacrifices to achieve fame and power? Will you embrace a foreign prince's offer or save your corrupt country from within? Weigh increasingly high stakes with each challenging decision.<br><br><strong>A HERO IS NOT MERELY BORN</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/ab25f9508d3e20b0721d0726e1251e0d.poster.avif?t=1741226613\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/ab25f9508d3e20b0721d0726e1251e0d.webm?t=1741226613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Hone your martial prowess in massive battles and relentless pursuits. The more you fight, the stronger you become. Delve into a vast arsenal of kungfu scriptures and gear to craft an ideal build, tailored through your customized leveling route.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/ffdb3dfbefe56fa1f3a3228bb173058d.poster.avif?t=1741226613\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/ffdb3dfbefe56fa1f3a3228bb173058d.webm?t=1741226613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>You had once stayed up past your bedtimes, huddled under covers, living the RPGs on SNES whose stories have stuck with you till today? Same for us! So much so that we’ve created an old-school Wuxia game with comparable features: strategic character leveling, turn-based combats, and most importantly, a vast array of characters and a gripping, heartfelt story.<br><br><strong>MAKE YOUR OWN NAME IN THE CHANGEABLE WULIN</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/d780724434f4a14f7077861488c4e4d5.poster.avif?t=1741226613\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/d780724434f4a14f7077861488c4e4d5.webm?t=1741226613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/d780724434f4a14f7077861488c4e4d5.mp4?t=1741226613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Harness and master the disciplines of martial arts, and make friends with a diverse cast of memorable characters along the way. Make a name for yourself and navigate difficult decisions that’ll forever change the course of the world.<br><br><strong>AN EXPANSIVE CAST OF DYNAMIC CHARACTERS</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/a00dd8a06f793e363cf88cde2d261f4c.poster.avif?t=1741226613\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/a00dd8a06f793e363cf88cde2d261f4c.webm?t=1741226613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Meet feuding clans and sects, brave patriots, twisted villains, and gruff old masters with remarkable kungfu skills.<br><br><strong>THE FATE OF JIANGHU RESTS IN YOUR HAND</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/07fa99a83cd177d67f930cb8e257b6c8.poster.avif?t=1741226613\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/07fa99a83cd177d67f930cb8e257b6c8.webm?t=1741226613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/07fa99a83cd177d67f930cb8e257b6c8.mp4?t=1741226613\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Face moral dilemmas, beyond simple choices of good versus evil, shaping both you and the path you’ll tread. Will you align with the court’s agents or the street heroes? Would you make “minor” moral sacrifices to achieve fame and power? Will you embrace a foreign prince's offer or save your corrupt country from within? Weigh increasingly high stakes with each challenging decision.<br><br><strong>A HERO IS NOT MERELY BORN</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/ab25f9508d3e20b0721d0726e1251e0d.poster.avif?t=1741226613\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1407450/extras/ab25f9508d3e20b0721d0726e1251e0d.webm?t=1741226613\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Hone your martial prowess in massive battles and relentless pursuits. The more you fight, the stronger you become. Delve into a vast arsenal of kungfu scriptures and gear to craft an ideal build, tailored through your customized leveling route.",
